{"type":null,"faqId":13996,"title":"如何省电？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">不使用荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">时，请按电源键关闭屏幕。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<a name=\"gen-id1.13.3.2.1.2.1\"></a><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">缩短屏幕待机时间。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<a name=\"gen-id1.13.3.2.1.2.2\"></a><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在主屏幕，点击<b>设置</b></span> <span>&gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">全部设置</span></b><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">显示</span></b><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">休眠</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，选择较短的屏幕待机时间。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<a name=\"figd0e3257\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.13.3.2.1.2.3.1\"></a><span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=44837\" width=\"529\" height=\"624\" alt=\"\" /></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<a name=\"gen-id1.13.3.2.1.3.1\"></a><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">降低屏幕亮度。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<a name=\"gen-id1.13.3.2.1.3.2\"></a><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在主屏幕，点击<b>设置</b></span><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">常用设置</span></b><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">亮度</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，拖动滑块降低屏幕亮度。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<a name=\"figd0e3278\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.13.3.2.1.3.3.1\"></a><span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=44838\" width=\"529\" height=\"422\" alt=\"\" /></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">使用耳机拨打电话、听音乐等。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">不需要使用蓝牙时，请关闭蓝牙功能。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<a name=\"figd0e3288\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.13.3.2.1.5.1.1\"></a><span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=44839\" width=\"527\" height=\"496\" alt=\"\" /></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">不需要使用无线局域网时，请关闭无线局域网连接。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<a name=\"figd0e3295\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.13.3.2.1.6.1.1\"></a><span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=44841\" width=\"529\" height=\"490\" alt=\"\" /></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">不需要使用</span><span>GPS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">服务时，请关闭</span><span>GPS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">功能。</span> \n</p>\n<a name=\"figd0e3302\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.13.3.2.1.7.1.1\"></a><span style=\"font-family:';font-size:10.5pt;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=44840\" width=\"529\" height=\"490\" alt=\"\" /></span>","faqTypeId":165,"faqType":"电池与充电","useful":0,"un